    <div class="column">
        <p>The only thing that doesn't make this a 10/10 is because of how short it is. You might think that's a petty reason for it, but right now, it's like watching a great library being built brick by brick. It already look magnificent, but for the love of books, the climax of this story is not even in the horizon yet! What is up with that <em>spoiler</em> girl who came late? Why is Sedona doing all this <em>spoiler?</em> What is that book Sedona gave Theo in the start of the series? Can Ohgga get even more cuter- I mean ehm.... well, the climax is definitely going to be something I look forward to enjoying in my life! I just need to survive them first until it comes.</p>
